HEADWORD: Sintoc
<hw>Sin"toc</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of spice
used in the East Indies, consisting of the bark of a species of
<gen>Cinnamomum.</gen></def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>sindoc</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

